1.# ./configure --prefix=/usr/local/apache2 --enable-module=so 
2.#make 
3.#make install
4.启动：#sudo /usr/local/apache2/bin/httpd -k start 
     启动时提示:  
        httpd: Could not determine the server's fully qualified domain name, using 127.0.0.1 for ServerName. 
     解决办法是在http.conf中加一行: 
        ServerName 127.0.0.1:80   或者ServerName localhost:80
5.停止：#sudo /usr/local/apache2/bin/httpd -k stop 
6.让Ubuntu开机自动启动apache. 
   1). 复制 /usr/local/apache2/bin/apachectl到/etc/init.d 
   2). 加载为服务 
       sudo update-rc.d apachectl defaults 

